This is first parameter: <atext name="param1" type="param">param1</atext>
This is second parameter: <atext name="param2" type="param">param2</atext>
This is first parameter at another location: <atext name="param1" type="param">param1</atext>
This is second parameter at another location: <atext name="param2" type="param">param2</atext>

Parent group's settings:
- Expand after typing delimiter(discard delimiter)
- Delimiters: Enter, Tab

With above Delimiters setting, it is possible to type space in parameter.
For example:
1. Type: testparam2first param,second param
2. Hit Enter key or Tab key

If parent group's settings:
- Expand after typing abbreviation
Parameter will be converted to Field after typing abbreviation.
